author: ehillenius
msg: Added separate example for the date picker that also displays the localized strings it has now (WICKET-754). FormInput is messy enough, and on the longer term we can add more date/ time related examples here if we want. But even without that, it has enough source for a nice read.

author: ehillenius
msg: WICKET-754 (Added support for localized months and weekdays in the date picker. By default pulls those strings from the Java distribution, so most locales should have decent support.)
